{"pageProps":{"post":{"mdxSource":"<img src=\"https://cdn.ipfsscan.io/weibo/large/005ZoLfCgy1ht1cckhaskj30wu0e6gtm.jpg\" />\n\n<h1>godot新增tilemap-layer节点</h1>\n<p>在此版本之前，如果要向 TileMap 添加图层，则必须在 Inspector 中添加它们。我们通过创建新的 TileMapLayer 节点来完全替换旧方法，从而简化了这一过程</p>\n<p>除了使用起来更直观之外，这现在更符合 Godot Engine 的总体设计理念。</p>\n<p>为方便起见，您可以直接在编辑器中一键将现有的 TileMap 节点转换为 TileMapLayer 节点。如果您愿意，目前仍支持已弃用的节点类型。</p>\n","frontMatter":{"readingTime":{"text":"1 min read","minutes":0.715,"time":42900,"words":143},"slug":"godot-release/4.3/godot4.3-新增tilemap-layer节点","fileName":"godot-release/4.3/godot4.3-新增tilemap-layer节点.md","date":"2024-08-26T00:00:00.000Z","tags":["godot"],"category":["godot-release"],"thumbnail":"https://cdn.ipfsscan.io/weibo/large/005ZoLfCgy1ht1cckhaskj30wu0e6gtm.jpg","draft":false,"keywords":["godot教程","godot中文教程","godot开发教程","godot更新日志"],"title":"godot4.3-新增tilemap-layer节点"}},"prev":{"date":"2024-08-26T00:00:00.000Z","tags":["godot"],"category":["godot-release"],"thumbnail":"https://cdn.ipfsscan.io/weibo/large/005ZoLfCgy1ht1c97a6m0j30ws0e6gr0.jpg","draft":false,"keywords":["godot教程","godot中文教程","godot开发教程","godot更新日志"],"title":"godot4.3-新的音乐资源节点","slug":"godot-release/4.3/godot4.3-新的音乐资源节点"},"next":{"date":"2024-08-26T00:00:00.000Z","tags":["godot"],"category":["godot-release"],"thumbnail":"https://cdn.ipfsscan.io/weibo/large/005ZoLfCgy1ht1cbmltlfj30wc0dmwiq.jpg","draft":false,"keywords":["godot教程","godot中文教程","godot开发教程","godot更新日志"],"title":"godot4.3-可视化编辑shader节点","slug":"godot-release/4.3/godot4.3-可视化编辑shader节点"}},"__N_SSG":true}